name: Space Tesla
description:
You wake up in the deep vacuum of space just floating and realize you aren't a person. You are a Tesla. You must collect enough fuel to make it back to Elon Musk on Earth and collect stars along the way.

Joystick/Arrow Keys- Move

W Key- Boost Up

S Key- Boost Down

Collect 100 Fuel to make it back to Earth 

Avoid Space Rocks

Collect Stars for a score(put amount in the comments)
